<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_197" id="98v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_197_r1l1"><expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> von Neẅenſtat <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dıener </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_197_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> hanns als du vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haſt von der <expan>drey<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l3">nu gen Prag gebracht ſein etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l4">laſſ dır dıe ſache befolhen ſein . als wır dır getrawen . Denn als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l5">du vns <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haſt . von <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſawrʒapf<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der ſeıd ʒu tawſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l6"><expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> ſey <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> etc von <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wıſſen wır noch niht ſunders </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l7">daʒ er vns vermeltt ſey daʒ er bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſcheden <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſey . <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l8">ſo <expan>empfelh<ex>en</ex></expan> wır dır . daʒ du dıch in <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſache niht ſlaheſt . es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l9"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> denn / daʒ du von den dreyn <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> oder ſuſt . ſölıch redlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l10"><expan>kuntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemeſt</expan> / daʒ wıſſenlıch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> daʒ er auch bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſchede<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l11"><expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> ſo laſſ dırs denn auch <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein vnd tu <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>deın<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l12">fleıſſ vnd ernſt / damıt v̈ber Jn denn auch gerıcht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_197_r1l13"><expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex></expan> ſıgıllo <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıciuıu<ex>m</ex></expan> / <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> margarete </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_197" id="98v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von Newenstat,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hanns, als du uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hast von der
                            <expan>drey<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die nu gen Prag gebracht sein etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>, und lass dir die sache befolhen sein,
                        als wir dir getrawen. Denn als du uns <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        hast von <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Sawrzapf<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> der seid zu Tawst
                            <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> sey <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc., von <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wissen wir noch niht sunders,
                        daz er uns vermeltt sey, daz er bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> scheden
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sey. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        so <expan>empfelh<ex>en</ex></expan> wir dir, daz du dich in
                                <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> sache niht slahest, es
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> denn, daz du von den dreyn
                                <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> oder sust sölich redlich
                                <expan>kuntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemest</expan>, daz wissenlich
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, daz er auch bey
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>schede<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>. So lass dirs denn auch
                                <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein und tu
                            <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dein<ex>en</ex></expan> fleiss und ernst, damit über in denn auch
                        gericht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri
                                civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Margarete. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
